ore.subscriber
Interface Flushable

All Known Implementing Classes:
CollectionChangeSubscription, PropertyChangeSubscription
interface Flushable

Listeners implement this interface so events can be buffered when a Subscriber does have a current CometConnection. When the Comet connection becomes available the events are flushed from the buffer.
